---
title: Hoisin Pork Bao with roast root veg and salad
description: Umami imbued hoisin pork fills fluffy bao buns in this exciting offering. A classic side like honey roasted veg gets an Eastern twist with the addition of toasted sesame seeds.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y25_R36_W21_IE_IEXSP38818-11_Main_high-38c28bcc.jpg
